1> create a maven project , skip archetype
	-groupId
	-ArtifactId
	-packaging war (very imp)
	
2>paste the <parent>,<properties>,<dependencies> from the boot project pom.xml
to the existing project pom.xml (cltr+s)

3> rt click on project -> maven -> update maven project -> force update

4> paste application.properties file in src/main/resources
	-make the neccessary changes for the properties value
	
5> copy paste the com.cdac.spring_boot
which will have 2 java file in it
	a>Application.java (Spring Boot Starter launch class)
	b>HibernateConfiguration.java (Hibernate java configuration class )
		-SessionFactory configuration @Bean
		-TransactionManagerFactory configuration @Bean
6> now copy paste WEB-INF folder in src/main/webapp folder
	which has following files and folders
		a> views folders
			- create all the required .jsp files here
		b> web.xml files
7> now create Model,(Entity class, Service,Dao)
	(steps are written inside the class)
8> now create controller class
(steps are written inside the class)
9> run you Application.java file as java application
10> open the browser and run the following url

http://localhost:8080/getAllCustomers